,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不会，你会直接拿到藤校终身教职的offer。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或者这么说，全世界的一流高校都会抢着给你教授的职位。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e睡醒了没有？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e醒了，就去复习吧，先定个小目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e把高考数学考个满分玩儿玩儿，你说呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562833030,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"097c9c03b85cfced0efcd50bbe437e57","url_token":"yi-ru-40-72","name":"易如","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/097c9c03b85cfced0efcd50bbe437e57","user_type":"people","headline":"无业游民","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562833030","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546151511,"updated_time":1546151511,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这里我理解“会被清华北大数学系保送吗”，指的是去清北的数学系读本科。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生证明出了哥德巴赫猜想猜想，99.9999999999%的可能性是和大多数民科一样，只是自己觉得证出来了，没可能被数学界承认是正确的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好了，这不还有0.0000000001%的可能性吗？如果真的是这样，起码他应该看过陈景润证明的1+2，看过潘承洞的《哥德巴赫猜想猜想》，看过怀尔斯证明菲尔马大定理的证明，等等等等。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说明这娃娃已经数学功底深厚了，那还去什么清北读书学习的本科，难道不是直接去当教授博导吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以题主的问题的答案是“否定”。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559439529,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"64b70caddf6e9c656bd2a0ae11f676a0","url_token":"yanb-14","name":"就叫我小豹子吧","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/23fd1f79d918959015f9be28cf284aa5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/23fd1f79d918959015f9be28cf284aa5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/64b70caddf6e9c656bd2a0ae11f676a0","user_type":"people","headline":"嗷呜嗷呜","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559439529","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545727020,"updated_time":1545727020,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e北大清华对你来说屈才了，教育部部长应该你来当，你把你的思维方式和论证方法编入教材，为国家培养更多像你这样的人才俊杰，在中华民族的历史上留下你伟大的名字才应该是符合你才能的方式。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560031667,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4c6644dcdcec98d6e49a9198232672b3","url_token":"tang-leefk","name":"唐LEEFK","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2cb727da7aab9d53c71b9e90c94a303d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2cb727da7aab9d53c71b9e90c94a303d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4c6644dcdcec98d6e49a9198232672b3","user_type":"people","headline":"内燃机，战列舰，GPU","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560031667","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545803336,"updated_time":1545803336,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不如同时发一份到arxiv？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560978032,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b4c1340a3275c87604bd54e40b2f76ae","url_token":"mu-wei-33-5","name":"牧威","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4536a78f54c6a309ad600d07b6ec4a2d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4536a78f54c6a309ad600d07b6ec4a2d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b4c1340a3275c87604bd54e40b2f76ae","user_type":"people","headline":"笨鸟久飞，也可入林。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560978032","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545903903,"updated_time":1545903903,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不是专搞数学的，不过就我浅薄的数学水平对哥猜的了解来说，提出这个问题，应该是还没证明出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e简单地说，目前哥猜的意义不在于哥猜本身，而在于证明的过程。之所以一直没有被证明，一般认为两种可能原因：一，没有足够好的工具，包括数学工具，也包括计算机；二，目前的工具已经够了，只是还没有人能提出足够严谨的证明思路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e话说回来，如果这位高中生真的证明了，那么不论是走第一条路——自己研发出了一个工具来证明，还是第二条路——设计出了足够严谨的证明思路。他所需要的，就不是清北本科的资源了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样的人才，从教育的角度来看，完全可以自己翻看教材学到极致；从结识数学大牛的角度来看，他不需要主动；从学历的角度来看，他的能力足够碾压“学历规则”。清北本科还有什么可以吸引他的么？帅哥美女？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前还没开箱，谁也不知道结果。如果真的证明出来了，建议这位同学提高一点眼界，不要只想着保送清北本科，起码往殿堂看看；如果假的，也不要灰心，因为哥猜就像希尔伯特说费尔马大定理“一只会下金蛋的母鸡”，你不一定要想着吃这只母鸡的肉，能让它下出蛋来，也是莫大的本事。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562095638,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c0ffbc8208cdcd9